{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setEmails:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSArray","text":"NSArray","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"emails","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"emails","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Array of email address strings. Each must be a valid email format.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Associates multiple email addresses with the current device for omnichannel","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"email campaigns. This is useful when users have multiple email addresses"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(work, personal, etc.) and want to receive communications on all of them."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All provided emails will be linked to the same device and user ID,"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"enabling unified targeting across all addresses.","type":"text"}]},{"anchor":"Example","text":"Example","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Register multiple emails from user profile:"}]},{"code":["class UserProfileManager {","","    func syncEmailsFromProfile(_ profile: UserProfile) {","        var emails: [String] = []","","        if let primary = profile.primaryEmail {","            emails.append(primary)","        }","        if let secondary = profile.secondaryEmail {","            emails.append(secondary)","        }","        if let work = profile.workEmail {","            emails.append(work)","        }","","        guard !emails.isEmpty else { return }","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setEmails(emails)","","        \/\/ Update tags with email count","        Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","            \"email_count\": emails.count,","            \"has_work_email\": profile.workEmail != nil,","            \"has_multiple_emails\": emails.count > 1","        ])","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setemails:"]}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"Registers multiple email addresses associated with the current user.","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setEmails:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setEmails:","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"symbolKind":"method","title":"setEmails:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setEmails:","kind":"identifier"}]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setEmails:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setEmails:":{"title":"setEmails:","type":"topic","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setemails:","abstract":[{"text":"Registers multiple email addresses associated with the current user.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setEmails:","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setEmails:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"